# Cloudflare Pages: real 404 for any unmatched path.
#
# Static prerendered routes (/, /impressum, /datenschutz, /bav-rechner,
# /etf-vs-bav, /riester-rechner, /altersvorsorgedepot-rechner,
# /riester-vs-altersvorsorgedepot, /basisrente-rechner,
# /private-rentenversicherung-rechner, /rente-netto-berechnen,
# /altersvorsorgeprodukte-vergleichen, /rentenluecke-rechner) take precedence
# over _redirects, so this catch-all only fires for genuinely-unknown URLs.
#
# Avoid the legacy "/* /index.html 200" rule, which triggers CF error 10021
# (infinite loop). The shape below — rewrite to /404.html with HTTP status 404
# — is the documented Cloudflare Pages pattern for SPAs that ship a real
# 404 page. The body is dist/404.html (prerendered with noindex,follow, the
# right canonical, and route-specific head tags).
#
# Live verification: `curl -sI https://rentenwiki.de/<unknown-url>` must show
# HTTP/1.1 404 after deploy.
/*  /404.html  404
